{"tid":1040555,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"BIG BANG勝利遭審8hrs憔悴離開警局","createTime":"2019-02-28T07:31:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-28T16:11:40.000Z","uid":74065,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"58d575668011ad461b673d9f6b42ecc6c3597acf","tid":1040555,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T07:31:50.000Z","msg":"南韓BIGBANG成員勝利近來遭捲入性招待、毒品交易等醜聞，為了證明清白，他27日晚間9點（台灣時間8點）親赴警局接受調查，歷經8個小時半的偵測，他在28號凌晨5點半（台灣時間4點半）離開警局，臉上佈滿憔悴神情，面對媒體追問，他正面回應「不論是何時叫我來，我都會誠實地接受調查」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3927/d3927358.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3927%2Fd3927358.jpg&h=405d0c1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲勝利28日早上結束調查，神情憔悴。（圖／翻攝自OBS）<br />\n<br />\n勝利28日凌晨5點半左右邁出警局，臉上掛著暗沈黑眼圈，看得出來已經精疲力盡，他表示，已經接受所有相關調查，尤其是毒品的毛髮檢測，任何一個該調查的部分，他都展現最高配合度，「現在大眾雖然對我很不滿，但我也希望能儘早揭開事實，盡了全力配合，不論是何時叫我來，我都會誠實地接受調查。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3927/d3927357.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3927%2Fd3927357.jpg&h=997d1eb1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼勝利主動接受調查，還是被韓網罵翻天。（圖／翻攝自naver、OBS）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3927/d3927356.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3927%2Fd3927356.jpg&h=55d71e2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n據韓媒報導，勝利當晚接受第一輪毛髮檢測，初步結果為陰性（沒有吸毒嫌疑），剩下相關的證據將轉交給「國立科學調查院」緊密調查，結果最快在1、2週後出爐。然而，勝利離開警局後，大眾並未因此放過他，新聞下方留言充斥負面字句「無法相信警方的調查結果」、「你當然沒吸毒，因為你是餵毒的人」。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3927/d3927360.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3927%2Fd3927360.jpg&h=aa352b6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲YG 28日一早找來銷毀文件的貨車。（圖／翻攝自chosun）<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">此外，又有媒體獨家直擊，YG在28日清晨7點左右叫來2輛文件銷毀貨車，除了一般文件外，還有疑似有手機、電腦等物件。對此YG表示，是每月都會進行的定期文書清理。</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n入冊先定入伍先呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4846b6c1fe687f7f82c85761d70962e8fa4be744","tid":1040555,"uid":43061,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T07:35:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />國際犯毒天團"},{"pid":"5a23dd7f209090a175c15267979acef578f521a9","tid":1040555,"uid":74065,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T07:36:37.000Z","msg":"取消3月9日-10日在大阪以及17日在雅加達的演唱會<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9328c0ec0dac38719cbabe3707cd294cd1c4a920","tid":1040555,"uid":223790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T07:42:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0951709eae0a199f08b4e0d10700afddd1cec33c","tid":1040555,"uid":223790,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T07:42:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3796a2b6f75493b97018d2309c1848511487e38b","tid":1040555,"uid":223790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T07:42:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f5cd4e6022f6cefbaa1a0fddfa7fda0ec9dff8b5","tid":1040555,"uid":22